hts-to-and-from-israel-through-october-24/00000191-36e7-df1b-adf1-fee7527a0000</guid></item><item><title>“这是犹太复国主义与圣战”：尽管真主党威胁，该组织仍在鼓励撤离的以色列人收复北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/despite-hezbollah-threat-this-group-encourages-evacuated-israelis-to-reclaim-the-north/00000191-367b-d1ef-a1f3-377b61a60000</link><description>他们生活在以色列可能是受威胁最严重的地区，但北部的一群活动人士厌倦了国家的无所作为，正在鼓励他们疏散的邻居返回家园。这对于当代犹太复国主义来说会是一个具有开创性的时刻吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:17:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/despite-hezbollah-threat-this-group-encourages-evacuated-israelis-to-reclaim-the-north/00000191-367b-d1ef-a1f3-377b61a60000</guid></item><item><title>死去的以色列年轻人的褪色照片和到处都是灰尘：参观新星遗址</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/faded-photos-of-dead-young-israelis-and-dust-everywhere-a-visit-to-the-nova-site/00000191-3283-d940-a991-f7d7afc90000</link><description>大屠杀发生十个月后，只有来自加沙的炮火打破了寂静，雷伊姆基布兹附近自发的纪念角落突然出现</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/faded-photos-of-dead-young-israelis-and-dust-everywhere-a-visit-to-the-nova-site/00000191-3283-d940-a991-f7d7afc90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何帮助建立并继续支持赤道几内亚的残暴政权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-israel-helped-set-up-and-continues-to-support-equatorial-guineas-brutal-regime/00000191-362c-d1ef-a1f3-377d25420000</link><description>以色列帮助了许多残酷的独裁政权。但仍然很难相信它在赤道几内亚的行动</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-israel-helped-set-up-and-continues-to-support-equatorial-guineas-brutal-regime/00000191-362c-d1ef-a1f3-377d25420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙汗尤尼斯发起地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-operation-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-3608-de93-a799-7faf11be0000</link><description>在告诉一些居民撤离该城市一天后，以色列国防军宣布将第三次在汗尤尼斯开展行动</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-operation-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-3608-de93-a799-7faf11be0000</guid></item><item><title>盗窃、殴打和无休止的骚扰：谁将成为这些定居者的下一个受害者？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theft-beatings-and-ceaseless-harassment-who-will-be-these-settlers-next-victim/00000191-31cf-dedb-abb7-77ef54ce0000</link><description>一位 62 岁的祖母和她的侄子在南希伯伦山遭到殴打。他们的七只羊被偷了。一名外国活动人士的护照被没收。十个月来，几乎每天都有定居者袭击无助的巴勒斯坦牧羊人</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theft-beatings-and-ceaseless-harassment-who-will-be-these-settlers-next-victim/00000191-31cf-dedb-abb7-77ef54ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的敌人寻求报复，但不会严厉到发动全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-enemies-seek-revenge-but-not-so-harsh-as-to-start-all-out-war/00000191-32f0-d2d3-af9d-3ef5c6750000</link><description>以色列公众正在认真对待伊朗和真主党对国内前线发动导弹和无人机袭击的威胁，内塔尼亚胡不愿意做出使战争更接近结束的协议所需的妥协</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-enemies-seek-revenge-but-not-so-harsh-as-to-start-all-out-war/00000191-32f0-d2d3-af9d-3ef5c6750000</guid></item><item><title>当内塔尼亚胡等待特朗普时，以色列的拆除人员政府破坏了西方的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/while-netanyahu-waits-for-trump-israels-demolition-crew-govt-undermines-western-support/00000191-33a6-daa8-a3b7-f7f7d2340000</li