fd-33bf18be0000</link><description>司法部调查人员表示，总警司阿米特·波拉克 (Amit Pollak) 本周因 4 月份在内塔尼亚胡家外暴力逮捕老年抗议者而受到讯问，他还就手机损坏问题撒了谎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/hadera-police-chief-under-investigation-for-assault-also-suspected-of-obstructing-probe/00000191-3337-d6fe-a9fd-33bf18be0000</guid></item><item><title>打开电视就可以看到以色列自 10 月 7 日以来道德的恶化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-09/ty-article/.highlight/to-see-israels-moral-deterioration-since-october-7-just-turn-on-your-television/00000191-3272-de61-adb5-b27e20cc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他的盟友将作为亵渎以色列社会以推进民族主义弥赛亚议程的人而载入史册。像第 12 频道新闻首席执行官阿维·韦斯这样的人物将因教唆这场毁灭而被埋葬，不是因为意识形态，而是因为对收视率的不懈追求</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-09/ty-article/.highlight/to-see-israels-moral-deterioration-since-october-7-just-turn-on-your-television/00000191-3272-de61-adb5-b27e20cc0000</guid></item><item><title>“之前我因为安全局势而放弃了一次以色列之行。我没有时间再等了&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对父子去朝圣，参观圣地并品尝 Shakshuka，一名匈牙利侨民向以色列的新移民传达了令人鼓舞的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</guid></item><item><title>“他们的头顶上没有屋顶”：数千名加沙人逃离汗尤尼斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</link><description>以色列军队再次呼吁汗尤尼斯许多社区的居民前往马瓦西安全区。加沙紧急服务部门称，以色列周四袭击了舒贾耶两所学校，造成至少 15 人死亡，至少 30 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列艺术家在真主党无尽的无人机下拍摄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</link><description>在海法艺术博物馆，艺术家哈达尔·赛凡 (Hadar Saifan) 为一个孤独的地区发声。此外，一部纪录片讲述了诺瓦音乐节的悲惨故事，一本新书探讨了战时的女权主义</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:17:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯世界在社交媒体上赞扬叶海亚·辛瓦尔登上哈马斯的最高宝座</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</link><description>随着长达10个月的加沙战争的持续，强硬派被认为是一个不错的选择，但一些评论员担心，此举让这位10月7日建筑师有更大的许可与以色列“战斗到最后一个孩子”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹德国的犹太共产主义者、犹太复国主义者和反犹太复国主义者：艺术家莉亚·格伦迪格的一生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</link><description>在新兴以色列事业蓬勃发展的鼎盛时期，蜚声国际的犹太裔德国画家莉亚·格伦迪格 (Lea Grundig) 抛下一切回到了东德，在那里他的光芒逐渐褪去。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</guid></item><item><title>奇迹产业：10 月 7 日之后，谁会从超自然故事的扩散中受益？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</link><description>奈蒂沃特是否因三个正义之人出现在恐怖分子面前而免遭屠杀？ 10 月 7 日的破裂催生了数百个关于奇迹和救赎的故事，证明了需要从混乱中创造意义——当然还有一些人希望利用这种情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</guid></item></channel></rss>